"1/2 cup apricot preserves","1/4 cup stone-ground mustard","2 tablespoons chopped fresh flat-leaf parsley","2 tablespoons chopped fresh mint","2 teaspoons Champagne or white wine vinegar","2  (18-ounce) Cornish hens, skinned and quartered","1/4 teaspoon kosher salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","  Cooking spray"